1. *Sata* je otkucala. (The clock has struck.)
2. *Satovi* su nam odmjerili vrijeme. (The clocks have measured our time.)
3. *Satu* sam morao popraviti. (I had to repair the clock.)
4. Posjetili smo *satnicu* u gradu. (We visited the clock-tower in the city.)
